{"tid":886564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個班房尷尬時刻","createTime":"2018-11-02T07:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T12:23:35.000Z","uid":199869,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"54c36b4683aa109481bd7997dded662c7033ad04","tid":886564,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不論系中學定大學 上堂不時都會攰得濟訓着咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時訓得好舒服嗰陣 會無啦啦一下札醒 彈咗起身 好似人地受驚嚇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但明明唔係發緊夢 又冇人鬧我訓教 老師又唔係突然大聲講野 唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但因為成個人坐直咗 動作好大 次次則邊啲同學都望住我 以為我咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實我只係無啦啦札醒左 唯有呃佢地我發緊惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e67e10572c1cb5f99d33c050836b0f46b20514","tid":886564,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"系XD"},{"pid":"dcdb2e9de27b14516efd24b4c59834acebbda87c","tid":886564,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:46:44.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"86bad3688e647e1cab7e19d3b79ffd67f3d91245","tid":886564,"uid":199869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c9e3c353802d2386aaea084bc054270a26d804bc","tid":886564,"uid":199869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"90e67e10572c1cb5f99d33c050836b0f46b20514","tid":886564,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:44:44.000Z","msg":"系XD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"系你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d8a7093e8922ac0edd96b31b654573e2347ce4","tid":886564,"uid":43718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3